{"type":null,"faqId":47181,"title":"如何延长手机待机时间？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{color:#333333;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">不使用手机时，请关闭屏幕。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">缩短屏幕休眠时间。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">降低屏幕亮度。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">降低音量。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">关闭来电振动。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">不使用 4G 网络时，请切换到 2G/3G 网络。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">不使用移动网络、蓝牙、WLAN 或 GPS 时，下拉状态栏关闭对应的快捷开关。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n <span class=\"s2\">可以通过超级省电模式延长待机时间：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">进入“设置”界面，点击“省电管理”，勾选超级省电模式，点击“开启”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">华为会在官网发布最新软件版本，请进入</span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm%22 \\o %22 \"><span class=\"s2\">华为官网软件下载地址</span></a><span class=\"s2\">根据型号查询下载；或通过在线升级进行手机软件版本更新，以获得更好的使用体验。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">若问题依然存在，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":133,"faqType":"电池与充电","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2748","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Battery-Charging","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445219082000,"seriesProductName":"TIT-AL00,TIT-CL10,TIT-TL00","visitedTimes":136,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"待机时长,待机时间,续航时间","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}